thread.title_full: Zankyou evaluado por Erin Waters and Maurice Crallie

author: Erin Waters and Maurice Crallie
title: Erin Waters and Maurice Crallie
text: I just wanted a website that people would donate money to a honey-fund. This website is a little more than that. It was a bit difficult to navigate at first. We just planned an elopement in Hawaii and this website would be a lot handier for an elaborate wedding.
